hi.title: अधिक नई बैटमैन
hi.description:
बैटमैन ब्रेव और द बोल्ड ईस्टर एग्स। क्लेफेस टीज़र 2026 का पहला लुक, नए डीसीयू बैटमैन संदर्भ, नया जोकर, ब्लैक कैनरी, ब्लैक मास्क और अन्य बैटमैन खलनायक। सुपरमैन और मैन ऑफ़ टुमॉरो क्रॉसओवर और रॉबर्ट पैटिंसन द बैटमैन 2 का टीज़र ► https://bit.ly/AwesomeSubscribe
क्लेफेस जोकर ईस्टर एग्स https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pJzSPvhBfts&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwCLH9RIm-7ui56ameRYmdQ&index=3&pp=gAQBiAQB
एलियन अर्थ एपिसोड 6 का ट्रेलर https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wz8AA4anLJ0&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczzNwEARuHxVretci623PP2b&index=7&pp=gAQBiAQB

सुपरमैन 2: मैन ऑफ़ टुमॉरो का टीज़र https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e4UIKL0G0Ek&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwCLH9RIm-7ui56ameRYmdQ&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
एवेंजर्स डूम्सडे का ट्रेलर https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fusy_tKT1QE&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB0gcJCcYJAYcqIYzv
पीसमेकर सीज़न 2 एपिसोड 3 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vK3Ij4_Mm5M&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwCLH9RIm-7ui56ameRYmdQ&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB0gcJCcYJAYcqIYzv
स्पाइडर-मैन ब्रांड न्यू डे ट्रेलर https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B_59lBNjosE&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczxQXxyV_2D8kuEs_QsuQIyJ&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
फैंटास्टिक फोर का पोस्ट क्रेडिट सीन https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bS0k5LEl3-w&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
सुपरमैन ईस्टर एग्स https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QgoyaMHk2RQ&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwCLH9RIm-7ui56ameRYmdQ&index=2&pp=gAQBiAQB0gcJCdgJAYcqIYzv
आपातकालीन शानदार नए वीडियो https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FeOfhzu7ZdY&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczxQXxyV_2D8kuEs_QsuQIyJ&index=7

नए बैटमैन क्लेफेस के पहले लुक का विश्लेषण। नया जोकर, बैटमैन खलनायक संदर्भ और छिपे हुए विवरण। डीसीयू का नया बैटमैन। बैटमैन ब्रेव एंड द बोल्ड, जेम्स गन का साक्षात्कार।

सुपरमैन 2025 ईस्टर एग्स और छिपे हुए विवरण जो हमसे छूट गए। मिली एल्कॉक सुपरगर्ल सीन। नया सुपरमैन बनाम हेनरी कैविल सुपरमैन बदलाव। जेम्स गन का नया जस्टिस लीग। फोर्ट्रेस ऑफ़ सॉलिट्यूड, ब्रैडली कूपर जोर-एल कैमियो सीन, केलेक्स रोबोट, नए दृश्य। नए बैटमैन बदलाव और बैटमैन के लिए डीसी मूवीज़ की योजना की व्याख्या। नए फुटेज और दृश्य। फोर्ट्रेस ऑफ़ सॉलिट्यूड। सुपरमैन बनाम अल्ट्रामैन, ईविल सुपरमैन। ग्रीन लैंटर्न का पहला लुक। मिस्टर टेरिफिक क्रिप्टो सीन। सुपरमैन बनाम लेक्स लूथर, नया फुटेज, सुपरमैन लिगेसी 2025 का टीज़र। नया सुपरमैन सूट, द फ्लैश रिटर्न्स की व्याख्या। मिली एल्कॉक सुपरगर्ल। नई सुपरगर्ल बनाम पिछले संस्करण। सुपरगर्ल वुमन ऑफ़ टुमॉरो मूवी का टीज़र। डेविड कोरेंसवेट सुपरमैन, निकोलस हॉल्ट लेक्स लूथर की व्याख्या, लेक्स लूथर के पिछले संस्करणों जैसे मैन ऑफ़ स्टील, बैटमैन बनाम सुपरमैन, जस्टिस लीग से बदलाव। द अथॉरिटी। सुपरमैन लिगेसी प्लॉट और कहानी की व्याख्या। नई सुपरगर्ल की व्याख्या।

डेविड कोरेंसवेट सुपरमैन, रेचल ब्रोसनाहन लोइस लेन की व्याख्या। बैटमैन ब्रेव एंड द बोल्ड टीज़र और नए बैटमैन की घोषणा अगले साल की जाएगी। बैटमैन ब्रेव एंड द बोल्ड टीज़र और नए बैटमैन की घोषणा अगले साल की जाएगी। नाथन फ़िलियन ग्रीन लैंटर्न, हॉकगर्ल, मिस्टर टेरिफिक और कई नए जस्टिस लीग किरदार। नई जस्टिस लीग एनिमेटेड जस्टिस लीग टीम पर ज़्यादा क्यों आधारित है।

और भी कई डीसी और मार्वल ट्रेलर आ रहे हैं, एवेंजर्स 5 डूम्सडे ट्रेलर और जल्द ही और भी सुपरमैन मैन ऑफ़ टुमॉरो वीडियो! जैसे-जैसे हमें पीसमेकर सीज़न 2 के एपिसोड के दौरान और ईस्टर एग्स मिलेंगे, मैं और भी बैटमैन वीडियो बनाऊँगा!

ko.description:

새로운 배트맨 클레이페이스 첫 공개 분석. 새로운 조커, 배트맨 빌런 레퍼런스 및 숨겨진 디테일. DCU의 새로운 배트맨. 배트맨 브레이브 앤 더 볼드, 제임스 건 인터뷰 분석.

슈퍼맨 2025 이스터 에그 및 우리가 놓친 숨겨진 디테일. 밀리 알콕의 슈퍼걸 장면. 새로운 슈퍼맨 대 헨리 카빌 슈퍼맨 변화. 제임스 건의 새로운 저스티스 리그. 포트리스 오브 솔리튜드, 브래들리 쿠퍼 조엘 카메오 장면, 켈렉스 로봇, 새로운 장면. 새로운 배트맨 변화와 배트맨을 위한 DC 영화 계획 설명. 새로운 영상과 장면. 포트리스 오브 솔리튜드. 슈퍼맨 대 울트라맨, 사악한 슈퍼맨. 그린 랜턴 첫 등장. 미스터 테리픽 크립토 장면. 슈퍼맨 대 렉스 루터, 새로운 영상, 슈퍼맨 레거시 2025 티저. 새로운 슈퍼맨 슈트, 플래시 리턴즈 설명. 밀리 알콕 슈퍼걸. 새로운 슈퍼걸 대 이전 버전. 슈퍼걸 우먼 오브 투모로우 영화 티저. 데이비드 코렌스윗 슈퍼맨, 니콜라스 홀트 렉스 루터 설명, 맨 오브 스틸, 배트맨 대 슈퍼맨, 저스티스 리그 등 이전 버전의 렉스 루터와의 변화. 어쏘리티. 슈퍼맨 레거시 줄거리 및 스토리 설명. 새로운 슈퍼걸 설명.

데이비드 코렌스윗 슈퍼맨, 레이첼 브로스나한 로이스 레인 설명. 배트맨 브레이브 앤 더 볼드 티저와 새로운 배트맨은 내년에 발표될 예정입니다. 배트맨 브레이브와 볼드 티저, 그리고 새로운 배트맨은 내년에 발표될 예정입니다. 네이선 필리언, 그린 랜턴, 호크걸, 미스터 테리픽 등 새로운 저스티스 리그 캐릭터들이 등장합니다. 왜 새로운 저스티스 리그는 애니메이션 저스티스 리그 팀을 기반으로 할까요?

더 많은 DC 및 마블 예고편이 곧 공개됩니다. 어벤져스 5 둠스데이 예고편과 슈퍼맨 맨 오브 투모로우 영상도 곧 공개됩니다! 피스메이커 시즌 2 에피소드에서 이스터 에그가 더 많이 나오면 배트맨 영상도 더 많이 올릴 예정입니다!

バットマンの新作、クレイフェイスのファーストルックを徹底解説。新ジョーカー、バットマンの悪役に関する言及と隠された詳細。DCUの新バットマン。バットマン：ブレイブ＆ザ・ボールド、ジェームズ・ガン監督インタビューの詳細。

『スーパーマン2025』のイースターエッグと見逃した隠された詳細。ミリー・アルコックのスーパーガールシーン。新スーパーマン vs ヘンリー・カヴィルのスーパーマンの変化。ジェームズ・ガン監督の新ジャスティス・リーグ。孤独の砦、ブラッドリー・クーパーのジョー＝エルのカメオ出演シーン、ケレックス・ロボット、新シーン。新バットマンの変更点とDC映画におけるバットマンの計画を解説。新映像とシーン。孤独の砦。スーパーマン vs ウルトラマン、邪悪なスーパーマン。グリーン・ランタン初公開。ミスター・テリフィックのクリプトシーン。スーパーマン vs レックス・ルーサー、新映像、『スーパーマン・レガシー2025』ティーザー。新スーパーマンスーツ、フラッシュ・リターンズ解説。ミリー・アルコックのスーパーガール。新スーパーガール vs 旧バージョン。スーパーガール・ウーマン・オブ・トゥモロー映画ティーザー。デヴィッド・コレンスウェット演じるスーパーマン、ニコラス・ホルト演じるレックス・ルーサーについて解説。『マン・オブ・スティール』『バットマン vs スーパーマン』『ジャスティス・リーグ』など、過去のレックス・ルーサーとの違い。『ザ・オーソリティ』。『スーパーマン・レガシー』のあらすじとストーリー解説。新スーパーガールについて解説。

デヴィッド・コレンスウェット演じるスーパーマン、レイチェル・ブロズナハン演じるロイス・レーンについて解説。『バットマン：ブレイブ・アンド・ザ・ボールド』のティーザーと『ニュー・バットマン』は来年発表予定。『バットマン：ブレイブ・アンド・ザ・ボールド』のティーザーと『ニュー・バットマン』は来年発表予定。ネイサン・フィリオン演じるグリーンランタン、ホークガール、ミスター・テリフィック、そして新たなジャスティス・リーグのキャラクターたち。『ニュー・ジャスティス・リーグ』がアニメ版ジャスティス・リーグ・チームをベースにしている理由。

DCとマーベルの予告編が続々登場。『アベンジャーズ5』ドゥームズデイ予告編、そして『マン・オブ・トゥモロー』の動画も近日公開！『ピースメーカー』シーズン2のエピソードでイースターエッグが追加されたので、バットマンの動画ももっとアップします！

snippet.title: The Equalizer 4 (2025) - First Trailer | Denzel Washington | Concept
snippet.description:
#theequalizer #theequalizer4 #denzelwashington 

McCall’s next chapter.

Editing, VFX, SFX, Thumbnail by @KHStudio please subscribe:
✅ YouTube: https://bit.ly/KHstudio

🎥 Attention viewers!

Please note that this video is a concept trailer created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes. I have meticulously incorporated various effects, sound design, AI technologies, movie analytics, and other elements to bring my vision to life. Its purpose is purely artistic, aiming to entertain and engage with the YouTube community. My goal is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through this trailer. Thank you for your support, and let's dive into the world of imagination! 🍿

⚖️  The Equalizer 4

Following the explosive success of The Equalizer 3, whispers across Hollywood hint that Denzel Washington could reprise his role as Robert McCall in an unexpected fourth installment. While many believed the third chapter closed the book on McCall’s vigilante journey, new reports suggest the franchise may not be finished just yet.

Insiders speculate that The Equalizer 4 would bring McCall out of his hard-earned peace and back into the shadows of justice. The story is rumored to revolve around international crime syndicates that target innocent communities — pulling McCall into a global fight bigger than any he’s faced before.

While no cast has been confirmed, fans are speculating about potential returning characters such as Dakota Fanning’s Emma Collins, introduced in the third film. Reports also hint at new adversaries — ruthless mercenaries and government operatives — designed to push McCall to his absolute limits.

Feel free to express your thoughts on this exciting project by leaving a comment below.

snippet.title: JUJUTSU KAISEN Season 3 - Official Teaser Trailer (English Subtitles)
snippet.description:
JUJUTSU KAISEN Season 3 will be streaming on Crunchyroll in January 2026!

Yuji Itadori is a boy with tremendous physical strength, though he lives a completely ordinary high school life. One day, to save a classmate who has been attacked by curses, he eats the finger of Ryomen Sukuna, taking the curse into his own soul. From then on, he shares one body with Ryomen Sukuna. Guided by the most powerful of sorcerers, Satoru Gojo, Itadori is admitted to Tokyo Jujutsu High School, an organization that fights the curses… and thus begins the heroic tale of a boy who became a curse to exorcise a curse, a life from which he could never turn back.

#IGN #Anime

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: Romeo Santos - Promise (Letra/Lyrics) ft. Usher
snippet.description:
🎵 Romeo Santos - Promise (Letra/Lyrics) ft. Usher

⏬ Stream “Promise” by "Romeo Santos ft. Usher" here: http://smarturl.it/ROSSpot?IQid=RSPA 

🎤 Song Lyrics: Romeo Santos - Promise  ft. Usher

[Verso 1: Romeo Santos]
He perdido el balance por tu amor
En tus manos yo caí, tienes control sobre mí
Tu cuerpo es la cárcel y yo un prisionero
Y jamás quiero salir, condenado y soy feliz

[Verso 2: Usher]
Try to keep my balance but I still fall
But how I fall so hard
Right into your arms, I swear girl
Wrapped inside you, baby, and it’s so warm, yeah, yeah, yeah
Love without a cause
Leaves me trapped inside my own bars

[Coro: Romeo Santos & Usher]
Quiero ser tuyo enterito pero tengo miedo
Prométeme que no me vas a dejar sin tu amor
(Talk to her Usher)
I’ll give you my heart, girl, but you got to promise
Prométeme, mami
Promise you'll hold me (Hold me)
Oh touch me (Touch me)
Love me
Way past forever

[Interludio: Romeo Santos & Usher]
Hasta siempre (Forever)
Woh-oh-oh
Escucha las palabras de Romeo
Oh-oh, oh
Yeah, man
Usher, baby
Romeo

[Verso 3: Romeo Santos]
Yo tan joven padezco del corazón
Y por tu amor sufriría mil años y con mucho honor (Don't die baby)

[Verso 4: Usher]
Uh-uh-uh
I'm trying to be calm but my chest keeps pounding
Trying to swim but it’s like I’m drowning
All I've got for you love
Oh baby

[Coro: Romeo Santos & Usher]
Quiero ser tuyo enterito pero tengo miedo
Prométeme que no me vas a dejar sin tu amor (Usher)
I’ll give you my heart, girl, but you got to promise
Ay, prométeme, mami
Promise you'll hold me (Hold me)
Oh touch me (Touch me)
Love me
Way past forever

[Interludio: Romeo Santos & Usher]
You need this in your life
Yeah, man
Two kings
Revolutionary
Hey yo' Romeo, talk to her
Hey

[Puente: Romeo Santos & Usher]
Temo que me dejes en el abandono
Y tú eres mi oxígeno y mi todo
But I realize that its worth running a race
When the finish line is you

[Coro: Romeo Santos & Usher]
Quiero ser tuyo enterito pero tengo miedo (Oh-oh, yeah, yeah)
Prométeme que no me vas a dejar sin tu amor (Oh-oh-oh-oh)
If I’ll give you my heart, girl, you got to promise
(Promise that you'll love me, baby)
Promise you'll hold me
Touch me (Oh touch me)
Love me (Oh-oh-oh)
Way past forever

[Outro: Romeo Santos & Usher]
Quiero ser tuyo enterito pero tengo miedo
(Turn the lights off)
Prométeme que no me vas a dejar sin tu amor

...........................................................................................

Lyric video for "Promise" by "Romeo Santos ft. Ushe" on Dope Music

snippet.title: Juan Gabriel - Así Fue (Letra)
snippet.description:
💟 Juan Gabriel - Así Fue 

⇨ Escucha nuestra Playlist: 💗 https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6goqsAnH1QY1FYt3hw9JZgQCbJUVJGM5&si=i0_pe_KLAKuOp6Y0

🌟 Escucha: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLZ0hz9KHThgnFWgWswXFz9WGALfrLuXht&si=rpU8x492aS_e5aBZ

💗 Romantic Music Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/playlist/0R4Z2Q6b496QOgcTdRfEy4?si=rK4ZLAf-Q0WiyyATEGByCQ

Juan Gabriel:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/soyjuangabriel_?igsh=bndnMDkwcDJodG00

Encuentranos:
https://www.instagram.com/letras4k_

🎤 Letra:

Perdona si te hago llorar
Perdona si te hago sufrir
Pero es que no está en mis manos
Pero es que no está en mis manos
Me he enamora'o
Me he enamora'o
Me enamoré

Perdona si te causo dolor
Perdona si te digo adiós
¿Cómo decirle que te amo?
¿Cómo decirle que te amo?
Si me ha preguntado
Yo le dije que no
Yo le dije que no

Soy honesto con ella y contigo
A ella la quiero y a ti te he olvidado
Si tú quieres, seremos amigos
Yo te ayudo a olvidar el pasado

No te aferres
Ya no te aferres
A un imposible
Ya no te hagas
Ni me hagas más daño
Ya no


Tú bien sabes que no fue mi culpa
Tú te fuiste sin decirme nada
Y a pesar que lloré como nunca
Ya no seguías de mí, enamorada

Luego te fuiste
Y que regresabas
No me dijiste
Y sin más nada
¿Por qué? No sé
Pero fue así
Así fue

Te brindé la mejor de las suertes
Yo me propuse no hablarte y no verte
Y hoy que has vuelto, ya ves, solo hay nada
Ya no debo, no puedo quererte

Ya no te amo
Me he enamora'o
De un ser divino
De un buen amor
Que me enseñó
A olvidar
Y a perdonar

Soy honesto con ella y contigo
A ella la quiero y a ti te he olvidado
Pero si tú quieres, seremos amigos
Yo te ayudo a olvidar el pasado

No te aferres
Ya no te aferres
A un imposible
Ya no te hagas
Ni me hagas más daño
Ya no

No, no, no, no-no
No, no, no, no-no
Na-na, na-na, ra, na-ra
Oh, no

#JuanGabriel #AsíFue #RomanticMusic

About Counter-Strike 2 (from its Steam page):
For over two decades, Counter-Strike has offered an elite competitive experience, one shaped by millions of players from across the globe. And now the next chapter in the CS story is about to begin. This is Counter-Strike 2.

A free upgrade to CS:GO, Counter-Strike 2 marks the largest technical leap in Counter-Strike’s history. Built on the Source 2 engine, Counter-Strike 2 is modernized with realistic physically-based rendering, state of the art networking, and upgraded Community Workshop tools.

In addition to the classic objective-focused gameplay that Counter-Strike pioneered in 1999, Counter-Strike 2 features:

All-new CS Ratings with the updated Premier mode
- Global and Regional leaderboards
- Upgraded and overhauled maps
- Game-changing dynamic smoke grenades
- Tick-rate-independent gameplay
- Redesigned visual effects and audio
- All items from CS:GO moving forward to CS2

The Counter-Strike esports scene is one of the biggest and most popular of them all, and have been for over 20 years! For CS2, BLAST Premier are dedicated to bringing you the most exciting and enjoyable viewing experience that the pro CS2 scene has to offer! 💥

snippet.title: T-Pain ft. Akon - Bartender (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
♫ T-Pain ft. Akon - Bartender (Lyrics) 
⭐ Stream: 

🎤 Lyrics: T-Pain ft. Akon - Bartender

[Intro: T-Pain]
Yeah, uh-huh
Yeah, yeah

[Verse 1: T-Pain]
Broke up with my girl last night so I went to the club (So I went to the club)
Put on a fresh white suit and the mini-coupe sittin' on dubs (Sittin' on dubs)
I'm just lookin' for somebody to talk to and show me some love (Show me some love)
If you know what I mean, uh-huh
Everybody jockin' me as soon as I stepped in the spot (I stepped in the spot)
Two hundred bi***es in the building, ain't none of them hot (Ain't none of them hot)
Except for this pretty young thang that was workin' on the way, at the top (On the way, at the top)
Shawty, what is your name?


[Pre-Chorus: T-Pain]
Ooh, she made us drinks to drink, we drunk 'em, got drunk
And I think she thinks I'm cool
She gave me a wink, I winked back, and then I think that
We hit it off somethin' proper like

[Chorus: T-Pain]
I like the bartender (Ooh, if you lookin' for me)
I'm at the bar with her (Oh oh oh uh-huh, okay)
I like the bartender (Yeah, if you lookin' for me)
I'm at the bar with her (Oh oh oh uh-huh, okay)

[Verse 2: T-Pain]
Got a brand new girl so I'm feelin' all good inside (All good inside)
Feel like I put some brand new twenty-fours on a brand new ride (On a brand new ride)
Triple shot of Patron on the rocks with a little bit of lime (With a little bit of lime)
I'm just keepin' it real, uh-huh
Baby still workin' at the club so I'm gettin' in free (So I'm gettin' in free)
Wednesday night, I'm on the list, T-Pain plus three (T-Pain plus three)
Every time I hit the spot babygirl takin' care of me (Takin' care of me)
How do you think I feel?
[Pre-Chorus: T-Pain]
Ooh, she made us drinks to drink, we drunk 'em, got drunk
And now I know she thinks I'm cool
She gave me a wink, I winked back, and then I think that
We gon' have fun at my spot tonight

[Chorus: T-Pain]
I like the bartender (Ooh, if you lookin' for me)
I'm at the bar with her (Oh oh oh uh-huh, okay)
I like the bartender (Yeah, if you lookin' for me)
I'm at the bar with her (Oh oh oh uh-huh, okay)

[Verse 3: Akon & T-Pain]
Shorty, I'm sure you heard that I rarely ever come out (Ever come out)
'Less I'm in the M6, doin' tricks, freeway burnt out (Freeway burnt out)
Got a passenger side that's empty wantin' it to be your spot (Be your stop)
Put you on my Billboard, we can act like the charts, I can end up on top (And I end up on top)
Don't smoke, don't drink, that's why I don't be by the bar baby (Baby)
Just lookin' at you from a distance, lookin' like a goddamn star baby (Baby)
So my girl don't see me T-Pain, can I get those keys to the car? (Those keys to the car)
'Bout to go and bang bang boogie with my cutie and I'll see you tomorrow (I'll see you tomorrow)

[Pre-Chorus: T-Pain & Akon]
Ooh, she made us drinks to drink, we drunk 'em, got drunk
And now I know, she thinks I'm cool (She thinks I'm cool)
She gave me a wink, I winked back (Uh-huh)
And then I think that (Uh-huh)
We gon' have fun at my spot tonight (Oh, yeah, slide)

[Chorus: T-Pain]
I like the bartender (Ooh, if you lookin' for me)
I'm at the bar with her (Oh oh oh uh-huh, okay)
I like the bartender (Yeah, if you lookin' for me)
I'm at the bar with her (Oh oh oh uh-huh, okay)

snippet.title: Ricardo Arjona - Historia de Taxi (Letra/Lyrics)
snippet.description:
Ricardo Arjona - Historia de Taxi (Letra/Lyrics)

Follow Ricardo Arjona:
https://instagram.com/arjonaoficial
https://twitter.com/Ricardo_Arjona
https://www.facebook.com/arjonaoficial

Letra:

[Intro]
¡Taxi!

[Verso 1]
Eran las diez de la noche, piloteaba mi nave
Era mi taxi un Volkswagen del año 68
Era un día de esos malos donde no hubo pasaje
Las lentejuelas de un traje me hicieron la parada
Era una rubia preciosa, llevaba minifalda
El escote en su espalda llegaba justo a la gloria
Una lágrima negra rodaba en su mejilla
Mientras que el retrovisor decía: "Ve qué pantorrillas"
Yo vi un poco más

[Verso 2]
Eran las diez con cuarenta zigzagueaba en Reforma
Me dijo: "Me llamo Norma", mientras cruzaba la pierna
Sacó un cigarro algo extraño, de esos que te dan risa
Le ofrecí fuego de prisa y me temblaba la mano
Le pregunté: "¿Por quién llora?", y me dijo: "Por un tipo
Que se cree que por rico puede venir a engañarme"
"No caiga usted por amores, debe de levantarse", le dije
"Cuente con un servidor si lo que quiere es vengarse"
Y me sonrió

[Coro]
¿Qué es lo que hace un taxista seduciendo a la vida?
¿Qué es lo que hace un taxista construyendo una herida?
¿Qué es lo que hace un taxista enfrente de una dama?
¿Qué es lo que hace un taxista con sus sueños de cama?
Me pregunté

[Verso 3]
"Lo vi abrazando y besando a una humilde muchacha
Es de clase muy sencilla, lo sé por su facha"
Me sonreía en el espejo y se sentaba de lado
Yo estaba idiotizado, con el espejo empañado
Me dijo: "Doble en la esquina, iremos hasta mi casa
Después de un par de tequilas veremos qué es lo que pasa"
Para qué describir lo que hicimos en la alfombra
Si basta con resumir que le besé hasta la sombra
Y un poco más

[Verso 4]
No se sienta usted tan sola, sufro aunque no es lo mismo
Mi mujer y mi horario han abierto un abismo
Como se sufre ambos lados de las clases sociales
Usted sufre en su mansión, yo sufro en los arrabales
Me dijo: "Vente conmigo, que sepa no estoy sola"
Se hizo en el pelo una cola, fuimos al bar donde estaban
Entramos, precisamente él abrazaba una chica
Mira si es grande el destino y esta ciudad es chica
Era mi mujer

[Coro]
¿Qué es lo que hace un taxista seduciendo a la vida?
¿Qué es lo que hace un taxista construyendo una herida?
¿Qué es lo que hace un taxista cuando un caballero
Hoy se ve con su mujer en horario y esmero?
Me pregunté

[Outro]
Desde aquella noche ellos juegan a engañarnos
Se ven en el mismo bar
Y la rubia para el taxi siempre a las diez en el mismo lugar

snippet.title: Zac Brown Band - Butterfly (feat. Dolly Parton) [Official Music Video]
snippet.description:
Zac Brown Band - Butterfly (feat. Dolly Parton) [Official Music Video]

Subscribe Here! http://bit.ly/ZacBrownBandSub
Catch Us On Tour! https://zacbrownband.com/pages/tour
Zac Brown Band Merch! http://bit.ly/ZacBrownBandMerch
Listen to Our Albums! http://bit.ly/ZBBMusic
Listen to The Comeback (Deluxe): https://ZacBrownBand.lnk.to/thecomebackdeluxe

Keep Up With Zac Brown Band
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/zacbrownband
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/zacbrownband 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/zacbrownband
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@zacbrownband?lang=en
Website: http://www.zacbrownband.com

Lyrics:

Innocence doesn’t last for long
But whatever don’t kill you makes you strong
Night is always darkest right before the dawn
So you can let down your armor guard gotta
Make room for who you are
The calloused hands that had held on to your heart
Gotta be pulled apart

Like reflections on white powder snow
Your light was always bound to be shown
There’s a beauty in your eyes
It’s a wonder to behold

Butterfly, you will see
You’re so much stronger than you think you are
You just have to believe
You can fly, mend your wings
Any moment you can free yourself
And fly out of the darkness, butterfly

Every branch broke on your family tree, you know you’re
Better than what they couldn’t be
You don’t have to practice anything that they preach
Those that don’t matter often mind
And Those that mind don’t matter
Don’t you pass them by
Oh you’ll learn in time

Like reflections on white powder snow
Your light was always bound to be shown
There’s a beauty in your eyes
It’s a wonder to behold

Butterfly, you will see
You’re so much stronger than you think you are
You just have to believe
You can fly, mend your wings
Any moment you can free yourself
And fly out of the darkness, butterfly

There’ll be times when your faith is gone
Give it one more day
Keep holding on
Oh it’s not what they say
It’s what you believe
That’s gonna break the chains
Changing you to what you’re gonna be

Butterfly, now you see
You’re so much stronger than you think you are
Now that you believe
You can fly, spread your wings
And in the moment you will free yourself
Fly out of the darkness, butterfly
Fly out of the darkness
Butterfly

Director: Projectblackboxx 

#ZacBrownBand #DollyParton #Butterfly #LoveAndFear

snippet.title: Veyeida - Levy Falkowitz & Meilech Braunstein | וידע - לוי פלקוביץ ומיילך ברוינשטיין
snippet.description:
Everything in this world comes from Him. From the vastness of creation to the quiet details of each person’s life, nothing is outside His plan. Each of us carries struggles, tests, and moments that feel too hard to bear. But even then, we are held. Every breath, every step, every part of life is His work, His art. And when we see the full picture, one truth stands clear. He is the King.

Credits:
Performed by: Levy Falkowitz & Meilech Braunstein
Composed by: Duvid M. Braunstein
Music Produced & Arranged by: Yanki Steinmetz
Vocal Production: Avrumy Lunger 
Mix: Lipa Brauner
Video: Double Clap Studios
Cover Design: VigiGee
Project Management & Marketing: SolBlum

Special thanks:
Chilly Wagshal
Yoely Stern | Stage Productions

--

דו האסט אונז באשאפן
וואס אונז גלוסטען און דארפן
די סדר הבריאה איז דיינס

די תורה איז דיין ווילן
אז אונז זאלן ערפילן
די עבודה איז מיינס

די תרי״ג עיטין די תרי״ג עצות
מיין עבודה אין דיין בריאה איז נישט גרינג
איך קען נישט אליין טראג מיך אויף דיינע פלייצעס
שמרה נפשי ווי דוד המלך איך זינג

ויחד לאהבה וליראה ביידע
אונז זענען דא פאר דיר אין יעדע דור
יעדער פאר זיך האט זיין עקידה
אונזער'ס זעה און יצחק׳ס זכור

וידע כל פעול כי אתה פעלתו
ויבין כל יצור כי אתה יצרתו
ויאמר כל אשר נשמה באפו
ה' אלוקי ישראל מלך ומלכותו בכל משלה

--

Levy Falkowitz
Bookings: 732-908-0011
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/levyfalkowitz

Meilech Braunstein
Bookings: 929-437-7712
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/meilechbraunstein

--

iw.title: Veyeida - Levy Falkowitz & Meilech Braunstein | וידע - לוי פלקוביץ ומיילך ברוינשטיין
iw.description:
Everything in this world comes from Him. From the vastness of creation to the quiet details of each person’s life, nothing is outside His plan. Each of us carries struggles, tests, and moments that feel too hard to bear. But even then, we are held. Every breath, every step, every part of life is His work, His art. And when we see the full picture, one truth stands clear. He is the King.

Credits:
Performed by: Levy Falkowitz & Meilech Braunstein
Composed by: Duvid M. Braunstein
Music Produced & Arranged by: Yanki Steinmetz
Vocal Production: Avrumy Lunger 
Mix: Lipa Brauner
Video: Double Clap Studios
Cover Design: VigiGee
Project Management & Marketing: SolBlum

Special thanks:
Chilly Wagshal
Yoely Stern | Stage Productions

snippet.title: NUMBER GO UP | Balatro Song!
snippet.description:
‘Really Stupes, a song about Balatro, a game with no narrative?’ Ah, but what if it was actually less about Balatro and more a reflection on the nature of existing within a system centred on the constant chase for validation via the unending quest for higher numbers, and the futility of it all in the face of our finite existence as human beings? You know, classic Stupendium fodder. 
This project began as something small-scale to test out something large – a robotic motion control arm that I bought! I first thought about getting a motion control arm for a different project that actually fell through, but I couldn’t get it out of my head. I needed one!
So, this video is the debut of our newest team member Armando! He is a Cinebot Mini from Mark Roberts Motion Control, and I love him. He was very expensive, so expect to see him a lot more in future shoots. (Why yes, I do personify all of my equipment, you should meet Cameron the camera.)
This shoot was very much a trial by fire. We got trained to use the arm by the wonderful Nigel from Mark Roberts, but having our first real test of it be one continuous 3-and-a-half-minute camera move with about 60 different passes for different characters that need to be perfectly aligned may not have been the best idea I’ve ever had. Especially since the initial idea for this video was just, ‘what can I use the motion control arm for? I could play poker with myself!’ But hey, we made it work (barely) and in the next video, maybe we’ll just use Armando for a few shots instead.
Thanks to the whole crew that wrangled the arm and made this all possible, especially everyone that stayed up very late on the last shoot day to get everything finished. And special thanks to CK9C for the beautiful sax solo that I badly mimed along to! 
-----
Check out the full Stupendium originals playlist for all of my original songs!
STUPENDIUM ORIGINALS:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLVVOXbE6Ls1glsfzH9tldq-KqPI-g84LA
THE STUPENDIUM ON SPOTIFY:
http://bit.ly/Stupendify
THE STUPENDIUM ON iTunes:
http://bit.ly/StupendiTunes
-----
Video by The Stupendium and Paul Marke
Shoot coordinator: Lizzy CJ
Production Assistants: @LawlessMarshall  Nick Henderson
Table fabrication: Nick Henderson, The Stupendium, @OxyOxspring, GMCassie
Costume fabrication and sourcing: @LawlessMarshall  The Stupendium, Lizzy CJ
Prop fabrication and sourcing: @LawlessMarshall  The Stupendium, Lizzy CJ
Makeup: @LawlessMarshall 
Special thanks: Nigel Permane and Mark Roberts Motion Control

Beat produced by @sinimabeats 
Song mixed by ‪‪@OxygenBeats

❥ Canción: Fuerza Regida - TU SANCHO (Letra) || mi niña, alista tu maleta ahorita

aquí la letra para que cantes a todo pulmón:

[Verso 1]
Mi niña alista tu maleta ahorita
Quiero que te pongas bonita
Ya le marqué al pinche piloto, ya dile al tonto que ya te vas
Cabrona, buena pa' mentiras
Y esa boquita me fascina
Baby, tú eres para un loco, y como este loco no hay como yo

[Verso 2]
Qué bonito chingarte en las nubes, bandida
El piloto pura verga baja la mira
Terminamos en treinta y llegamos a Ibiza, aterrizamos sin prisa
Materiales son los que tú menos pedías
Los detalles enamoraron a mi niña
Hoy te dejo una cuenta de banco en las Islas, tú date vuelo

[Interludio]
Ah-ah
Uh

[Verso 3]
Qué bonita te miras, biеn mamacita sin calzón
No le cuentes a tu amiga quе la tengo como león
Calladita te ves más bonita
Pa' mirarnos otra vez, que no lo sepa tu güey
Sin pedos te espero, peléate con tu güey
Invéntate una razón pa' que no lo haga de pedo
Ni pedo, sin pedo, ¿ya qué? (Eh, eh, eh)

[Verso 4]
Qué bonito chingarte y más rico y de noche
Un palito en el aire y privado pa' Londres
Diferentes mujeres de varios sabores
Nomás no te me aloques
Mujeriego y coqueto, tengo mil amores
De hace tiempo te busco, mas no sé ni en dónde
Si me quieres, tendrás que aguantar los rumores
Nomás no te me aloques

[Outro]
Ey
Fuerza Regida
Jajaja
¿Ah?
Jaja

snippet.title: Dax - "You're The Problem" (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
[LYRICS BELOW] You're The Problem...Share if you can relate. Let's continue to make an IMPACT. I believe this one is truly important. Can't wait to perform it on tour! Click here for tickets:  https://daxofficial.com/tour

Go Listen on Repeat: https://dax.lnk.to/FromAMansPerspective

Follow DAX: @thatsdax
actor: @ sarahdevermont
Shot by: Logan Meis
Produced by: Lex Nour Beats

#youretheproblem #dax #relationship #couplestherapy #marriage 

LYRICS:

You don’t ever see me how I see myself 
and that’s a problem 
Your hate is a reflection of yourself 
And that’s a problem 
You claim you want respect 
But you don’t ever show it back 
I stay on the defense 
Because you’re always on attack 
You find a way to twist it 
And you always tell me lies 
Focus on my reaction 
And not what you did and why 
You’re stuck inside your ways
There ain’t no way I can correct 
I think that you’re the problem 
And I’m just another man 
This relationships d*ad

You stay listening to your friends 
Give you advice, but they’ve been single since the day that we met 
How they know better, but they struggle
and then keeping no man 
Misery loves company, and I’m invested in not paying your debt 
Thought you were ride or die 
You led me on for a country mile 
Love b*mbed me now my wounds are open and I’m forced to realize 
Can’t turn no hoe to a wife 
No matter how hard that I try

time itself is a commodity

with no promise of a tomorrow ah

Out of pocket responses, 
you disrespect me out in public 
If I’m being honest, 
you probably got it from your mama 
I don’t got no time to deal with the drama
I’m too busy 
trying to stack up these commas 
to be your punching bag 
and deal with your childhood trauma
Swipe on your dating apps
We’re done, cause 
there ain’t no changing that

If you made it this deep you're a real one. Thank you for continuing to allow me to use my platform to make an impact. Your support is appreciated more than you'll ever know and I will continue to prove that with my actions. I'm very excited. 2025 IS NOT OVER my best and most impactful work is on the way. I am putting everything into creating pieces we can all be proud of. We are the label! Like, comment, SHARE and let's continue to be the change we wish to see in the world. Love you all! Can't wait to see you on tour next month!

snippet.title: The Search for Minecraft's Lost Kingdom
snippet.description:
Before the Unstable SMP was filled with tens of thousands of players, three friends built a hidden city to hide their fortune. They called it Verdaria. Since then, both the city and the treasure have been lost to time... waiting for someone to finally find them. This is The Search for Minecraft's Lost Kingdom. 

Like ParrotX2 and his Unstable SMP series, where he is escaping Paragon / Proton: Minecraft's Most Secure Prison, or got hunted by a Minecraft Player who doesn't exist. This is a new and original Minecraft idea like HermitCraft or Lifesteal with Wemmbu, FlameFrags, or Spoke. Survival is harder than Hardcore Minecraft because PVP is on.

People in this video: @TheobaldTheBird @dragon_mc_ @Boosfer @mixiku_ @Derapchu @creakyv @Taejon @nezoshoki @Wifies @SomethingBlueYT 

This is a video on the Unstable Universe: a staged Minecraft server where ParrotX2, Wemmbu, Spoke, and FlameFrags tell stories in Minecraft.

snippet.title: Indie Games Are Perfectly Balanced With No Exploits!
snippet.description:
Welcome to a very special video. A deep dive into the mad process of what it feels like to be the spiffing brit. I decided to see if I could play some brand new indie games from small developers just for fun after picking them up in the steam summer sale. yet no matter how hard I tried the call of overpowered and broken bugs and glitches is too strong! So today the spiffing brit will be breaking 3 incredible indie games and one not so indie game that is a SECRET!!!! oooo what could it be, its like a video game loot box but instead its just video formatting. 

So can the spiffing Brit Break these games. Can He prove that they are in fact perfectly balanced with no exploits or will he simply become the villain that developers see him to be!

Todays games are
9 Kings: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2784470/9_Kings/
Tower Dominion: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3226530/Tower_Dominion/
Void War: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2853590/Void_War/
AND UNKOWN MYSTERY GAME 9000

snippet.title: Do NOT look at it..
snippet.description:
One Last Clip a horror game where you are locked inside a cinema. Your only way to escape is to follow the instructions of your task: Watch the same film clip repeatedly and search for flaws to break free. But this may sound easier than it is, every wrong decision will set you back. So be careful!

snippet.title: US Prototype Tanks Are Crazy
snippet.description:
Prototype tanks can be pretty powerful in War Thunder, and that is especially true for oscillating turret tanks like the American T54E1 medium tank. It has a rapid fire autoloader and a good sabot round, but fights overpowered tanks like the Turm III. I also talk about the upcoming T58 heavy tank.

Check the channel "About" section for the link to the creator of my profile picture.

Songs used (in order from first to last):
C&C: Generals Soundtrack

snippet.title: Tomb Raider
snippet.description: Lara Croft is the fiercely independent daughter of an eccentric adventurer who vanished years earlier. Hoping to solve the mystery of her father's disappearance, Croft embarks on a perilous journey to his last-known destination -- a fabled tomb on a mythical island that might be somewhere off the coast of Japan. The stakes couldn't be higher as Lara must rely on her sharp mind, blind faith and stubborn spirit to venture into the unknown.

snippet.title: Completing All Minecraft Advancements Blind (No Google or Help) - Day 7
snippet.description:
I'm trying to complete all of Minecraft's advancements without Google or anyone helping me, even chat. A blind playthrough!

I have a mod that removes the description of each advancement so I have to work out how to do them with only my brain, even the super weird ones that make no sense lol. Of course there are some advancements that I already know how to do but there are over 100 advancements and most of them I have never even seen done before. This might take me a while...

I'm playing on the latest Minecraft version 1.21.8

snippet.title: Teaching Bluff How To Play Slots!
snippet.description:
I’m giving away $50,000 you DON’T want to miss it!: http://codebrettski.com 

We are BACK at the Casino… with the man himself, Bluff! I’m showing this meatball how to play slots, how to run it up, and how to PRINT handpays! Thank you all so much for liking, subscribing, and dropping your thoughts in the comments. Even if you’re roasting me—I still love you. You’re all beautiful, and I truly appreciate every single one of you for riding along on this crazy journey.  Wish me luck, and I’ll see you in the next one! Let’s go to war.

Brettski adjusted his mirrored shades as the neon lights of the *Golden Mirage* pulsed in the desert night. Beside him, Bluff—a wiry skeptic with a poker face carved from stone—dragged his feet. “Slot machines are rigged,” he muttered.

“Only if you don’t know *how* to listen,” Brettski replied, tapping the side of his head. “Tonight, I show you the science of the spin.”

Inside, the casino roared. Bells, flashing lights, the scent of desperation. Brettski beelined for a row of vintage slot machines near the sports bar. “The ‘Lunar Luck 7s’. Loosest machines in the city. But only *this one* sings at midnight,” he whispered, pointing to a battered, unloved unit with a cracked cherry decal.

Midnight struck. Brettski fed in a crisp twenty, and on the third spin—**JACKPOT**. Sirens blared, coins rained. Bluff’s jaw dropped.

“Beginner’s luck,” Bluff scoffed, but his hand trembled as he sat down at the next machine.

Then came the *second* win. Then a third.

But something shifted.

A dark-suited man with earpiece and clipboard appeared behind them. “Mind stepping away for a quick word?” he asked. Brettski smiled tightly.

They were led into a back room—not security, not a lounge. Just a red door with no signage.

Inside, smoke hung in the air. A round table. Seven people with eyes like calculators stared at them.

“You weren’t supposed to beat the odds,” a woman in a velvet suit said. “You weren’t supposed to find the *pattern*.”

Bluff swallowed. “What pattern?”

Brettski looked grim. “The slots aren’t games. They’re **testing gates**.”

Bluff’s chair jolted—*bolted to the floor*. The room began to spin, machinery grinding underneath.

And just as Bluff shouted Brettski’s name—

**The red door slammed shut.**
**Lights out.**
**A voice echoed: “Let the next phase begin.”**

#slots #blackjack #gambling #casino #baccarat #roulette

However, unlike these legends, Brettski has thousands of years of stored ancient knowledge harvested by the elders, at skills such as Slot Machines, Roulette, Blackjack, Craps, Bubble Craps, Poker, and Baccarat.  Brettski's goal as a Professional Gambler is simple: own all of Las Vegas, using funds made by Gambling.  Subscribe to support his journey in world domination.

ko.title: 블러프에게 슬롯 게임 방법을 가르쳐드립니다!
ko.description:
5만 달러를 드립니다! 놓치지 마세요!: http://codebrettski.com

카지노로 돌아왔습니다... 바로 그 블러프와 함께! 이 미트볼에게 슬롯머신 하는 법, 슬롯머신 돌리는 법, 그리고 핸드페이 인쇄하는 법을 알려드릴게요! 좋아요와 구독, 그리고 댓글로 생각을 남겨주셔서 정말 감사합니다. 저를 혹평하시더라도, 저는 여전히 여러분을 사랑합니다. 모두 아름다우시고, 이 미친 여정에 함께해 주신 모든 분들께 진심으로 감사드립니다. 행운을 빌어주시고, 다음 여정에서 뵙겠습니다! 자, 전쟁터로 떠나볼까요?

브렛스키는 사막의 밤하늘에 *골든 미라지*의 네온 불빛이 깜빡이는 것을 보며 거울 선글라스를 조정했습니다. 그의 옆에는 돌로 조각한 포커페이스를 한 건장한 회의론자 블러프가 발을 질질 끌며 서 있었습니다. "슬롯머신은 조작돼 있어." 그가 중얼거렸습니다.

"듣는 *방법*을 모른다면 그럴 수도 있지." 브렛스키가 머리 옆을 두드리며 대답했다. "오늘 밤, 내가 스핀의 과학을 보여드리지."

카지노 안은 굉음으로 가득했다. 종소리, 번쩍이는 불빛, 절박함의 냄새가 진동했다. 브렛스키는 스포츠 바 근처에 늘어선 빈티지 슬롯머신으로 곧장 향했다. "'루나 럭 7'. 이 도시에서 가장 허술한 슬롯머신이지. 하지만 자정에 노래하는 건 *이* 슬롯머신뿐이야." 그는 금이 간 체리색 데칼이 붙어 있는 낡고 쓸모없는 기계를 가리키며 속삭였다.

자정이 밝았다. 브렛스키는 20을 깔끔하게 넣었고, 세 번째 스핀에서 — **잭팟**. 사이렌이 울리고 동전이 비처럼 쏟아졌다. 블러프는 입을 다물지 못했다.

"초심자의 행운이군." 블러프는 비웃었지만, 다음 슬롯머신에 앉는 그의 손은 떨렸다.

그러더니 *두 번째* 당첨이 왔다. 그리고 세 번째 당첨.

하지만 무언가가 바뀌었다.

어두운 정장에 이어피스와 클립보드를 착용한 남자가 그들 뒤로 나타났다. "잠깐 얘기 좀 할 수 있을까요?" 그가 물었다. 브렛스키는 씁쓸하게 미소 지었다.

그들은 뒷방으로 안내되었다. 보안실도, 라운지도 아니었다. 그저 표지판도 없는 붉은 문뿐이었다.

안에서는 연기가 자욱했다. 둥근 테이블. 계산기 같은 눈을 가진 일곱 사람이 그들을 응시했다.

"승산을 따내면 안 돼." 벨벳 정장을 입은 여자가 말했다. "*패턴*을 찾으면 안 돼."

블러프는 침을 꿀꺽 삼켰다. "무슨 패턴?"

브렛스키는 침울한 표정을 지었다. "슬롯머신은 게임이 아니야. **테스트 게이트**라고."

블러프의 의자가 덜컹거리며 바닥에 고정되었다. 방이 빙빙 돌기 시작했고, 아래에서 기계가 삐걱거리는 소리가 났다.

블러프가 브렛스키의 이름을 외치는 순간—

**붉은 문이 쾅 닫혔다.**
**불이 꺼졌다.**
**목소리가 울렸다. "다음 단계로 넘어가자."**

#슬롯 #블랙잭 #도박 #카지노 #바카라 #룰렛

브렛스키는 누구일까요? 브렛스키는 베가스 맷, 블러프, 데겐달트, 미스터 핸드 페이, 레이디 럭 HQ 등 고대 전설과 같은 프로 도박꾼입니다! 하지만 이러한 전설들과는 달리, 브렛스키는 슬롯머신, 룰렛, 블랙잭, 크랩스, 버블 크랩스, 포커, 바카라 등 고대인들이 수천 년 동안 축적해 온 지식을 보유하고 있습니다. 프로 도박꾼으로서 브렛스키의 목표는 간단합니다. 도박으로 번 돈을 이용해 라스베이거스를 전부 차지하는 것입니다. 그의 세계 정복 여정을 응원하려면 구독하세요.

es-US.title: ¡Enseñándole a Bluff cómo jugar a las tragamonedas!
es-US.description:
¡Estoy regalando $50,000 que no te puedes perder!: http://codebrettski.com

¡Estamos de vuelta en el Casino… con el mismísimo Bluff! ¡Le estoy enseñando a este imbécil cómo jugar a las tragamonedas, cómo gestionarlas y cómo IMPRIMIR pagos manuales! Muchas gracias a todos por darle a "me gusta", suscribirse y dejar sus opiniones en los comentarios. Aunque me estén tomando el pelo, los sigo queriendo. Son todos preciosos, y de verdad les agradezco a todos por acompañarme en este viaje tan loco. ¡Deséenme suerte y nos vemos en la próxima! ¡Vamos a la guerra!

Brettski se ajustó las gafas de sol de espejo mientras las luces de neón del *Golden Mirage* brillaban en la noche del desierto. A su lado, Bluff, un escéptico enjuto con cara de póquer tallada en piedra, arrastraba los pies. "Las tragamonedas están manipuladas", murmuró.

“Solo si no sabes *cómo* escuchar”, respondió Brettski, dándose un golpecito en la cabeza. “Esta noche te mostraré la ciencia del giro”.

Dentro, el casino rugía. Campanas, luces intermitentes, el aroma de la desesperación. Brettski se dirigió directo a una hilera de máquinas tragamonedas antiguas cerca del bar deportivo. “Las 'Lunar Luck 7s'. Las máquinas más flojas de la ciudad. Pero solo *esta* canta a medianoche”, susurró, señalando una máquina maltratada y abandonada con una calcomanía de cereza rota.

Dio la medianoche. Brettski metió un billete de veinte, y en el tercer giro: **JACKPOT**. Las sirenas sonaron, llovieron monedas. Bluff se quedó boquiabierto.

“Suerte de principiante”, se burló Bluff, pero le temblaba la mano al sentarse en la siguiente máquina.

Luego llegó la *segunda* victoria. Luego, una tercera.

Pero algo cambió.

Un hombre de traje oscuro, con auricular y portapapeles, apareció detrás de ellos. "¿Les importaría apartarse para hablar un momento?", preguntó. Brettski sonrió tensamente.

Los condujeron a una trastienda; no era de seguridad ni una sala de espera. Solo una puerta roja sin letreros.

it.title: Insegna a Bluff come giocare alle slot!
it.description:
Sto regalando 50.000 $ che NON vorrai perderti!: http://codebrettski.com

Siamo TORNATI al Casinò... con Bluff in persona! Sto mostrando a questo polpettone come giocare alle slot, come farle girare e come STAMPARE i pagamenti manuali! Grazie mille a tutti per aver messo "Mi piace", per esservi iscritti e per aver lasciato i vostri pensieri nei commenti. Anche se mi state prendendo in giro, vi amo comunque. Siete tutti bellissimi e apprezzo davvero ognuno di voi per avermi accompagnato in questo folle viaggio. Auguratemi buona fortuna e ci vediamo alla prossima! Andiamo in guerra.

Brettski si aggiustò gli occhiali da sole a specchio mentre le luci al neon del *Golden Mirage* pulsavano nella notte del deserto. Accanto a lui, Bluff, uno scettico nervoso con una faccia da poker scolpita nella pietra, si trascinava. "Le slot machine sono truccate", borbottò.

"Solo se non sai *come* ascoltare", rispose Brettski, dandosi un colpetto sulla tempia. "Stasera ti mostro la scienza del giro."

All'interno, il casinò ruggiva. Campanelli, luci lampeggianti, l'odore della disperazione. Brettski si diresse a passo svelto verso una fila di slot machine d'epoca vicino al bar dello sport. "Le 'Lunar Luck 7s'. Le slot machine più perdenti della città. Ma solo *questa* suona a mezzanotte", sussurrò, indicando un'unità malconcia e trascurata con una decalcomania a forma di ciliegia crepata.

Scoccò la mezzanotte. Brettski inseriva un venti nitido e al terzo giro... **JACKPOT**. Le sirene squillavano, le monete piovevano. Bluff rimase a bocca aperta.

"La fortuna del principiante", schernì Bluff, ma la sua mano tremava mentre si sedeva alla slot machine successiva.

Poi arrivò la *seconda* vincita. Poi una terza.

Ma qualcosa cambiò.

Un uomo in abito scuro con auricolare e blocco per appunti apparve dietro di loro. "Vi dispiace allontanarvi per una parola veloce?" chiese. Brettski sorrise a denti stretti.

Furono condotti in una stanza sul retro, non era la sicurezza, non era una sala d'attesa. Solo una porta rossa senza insegne.

All'interno, il fumo aleggiava nell'aria. Un tavolo rotondo. Sette persone con occhi come calcolatrici li fissavano.

"Non avreste dovuto battere le probabilità", disse una donna in abito di velluto. "Non avreste dovuto trovare lo *schema*."

Bluff deglutì. "Quale schema?"

Brettski assunse un'espressione cupa. "Le slot machine non sono giochi. Sono **cancelli di prova**."

La sedia di Bluff sobbalzò, *schiacciata a terra*. La stanza iniziò a girare, con i macchinari che scricchiolavano sotto.

E proprio mentre Bluff gridava il nome di Brettski...

**La porta rossa si chiuse di colpo.**
**Luci spente.**
**Una voce echeggiò: "Che la fase successiva abbia inizio."**

nl-NL.title: Bluffen onderwijzen: hoe je gokkasten speelt!
nl-NL.description:
Ik geef $ 50.000 weg, die je NIET wilt missen!: http://codebrettski.com

We zijn TERUG in het casino... met de man zelf, Bluff! Ik laat deze gehaktbal zien hoe je gokkasten speelt, hoe je hem opvoert en hoe je handbetalingen PRINT! Heel erg bedankt allemaal voor het liken, abonneren en het achterlaten van je mening in de reacties. Zelfs als je me afkraakt, hou ik nog steeds van jullie. Jullie zijn allemaal prachtig, en ik waardeer het enorm dat jullie allemaal mee hebben gereisd op deze gekke reis. Wens me succes en ik zie jullie bij de volgende! Laten we ten strijde trekken.

Brettski zette zijn spiegelende zonnebrillen recht terwijl de neonlichten van de *Golden Mirage* in de woestijnnacht opflitsten. Naast hem sleepte Bluff – een pezige scepticus met een uit steen gehouwen pokerface – zijn voeten. "Gokkasten zijn gemanipuleerd," mompelde hij.

"Alleen als je niet weet *hoe* je moet luisteren," antwoordde Brettski, terwijl hij op zijn voorhoofd tikte. "Vanavond laat ik je de wetenschap achter het draaien zien."

Binnen brulde het casino. Bellen, knipperende lichten, de geur van wanhoop. Brettski liep regelrecht naar een rij vintage gokkasten vlak bij de sportbar. "De 'Lunar Luck 7s'. De meest losse gokkasten van de stad. Maar alleen *deze* zingt om middernacht," fluisterde hij, wijzend naar een gehavende, onbeminde machine met een gebarsten kersenhouten sticker.

Middernacht sloeg. Brettski gooide een frisse twintig in, en bij de derde draai—**JACKPOT**. Sirenes loeiden, het regende munten. Bluffs mond viel open.

"Beginnersgeluk," spotte Bluff, maar zijn hand trilde toen hij aan de volgende machine ging zitten.

Toen kwam de *tweede* winst. Toen een derde.

Maar er veranderde iets.

Een man in een donker pak met oortje en klembord verscheen achter hen. "Wilt u even weggaan voor een kort gesprek?" vroeg hij. Brettski glimlachte gespannen.

Ze werden naar een achterkamer geleid – geen beveiliging, geen lounge. Gewoon een rode deur zonder bordjes.

Binnen hing er rook in de lucht. Een ronde tafel. Zeven mensen met ogen als rekenmachines staarden hen aan.

"Je had niet tegen de verwachtingen in moeten vechten," zei een vrouw in een fluwelen pak. "Je had niet het *patroon* moeten vinden."

Bluff slikte. "Welk patroon?"

Brettski keek grimmig. "De gokkasten zijn geen spelletjes. Het zijn **testpoortjes**."

Bluffs stoel schokte – *vastgeschroefd aan de vloer*. De kamer begon te draaien, machines knarsten eronder.

En net toen Bluff Brettski's naam riep—

**De rode deur sloeg dicht.**
**Licht uit.**
**Een stem echode: "Laat de volgende fase beginnen."**

hi.title: ब्लफ़ को स्लॉट खेलना सिखाना!
hi.description:
मैं $50,000 दे रहा हूँ, आप इसे मिस नहीं करना चाहेंगे!: http://codebrettski.com

हम कैसीनो में वापस आ गए हैं... उस शख्स के साथ, ब्लफ़! मैं इस मीटबॉल को दिखा रहा हूँ कि स्लॉट कैसे खेलें, उसे कैसे चलाएँ, और हैंडपे कैसे प्रिंट करें! लाइक करने, सब्सक्राइब करने और कमेंट्स में अपने विचार देने के लिए आप सभी का बहुत-बहुत शुक्रिया। भले ही आप मुझे चिढ़ा रहे हों—मैं फिर भी आपसे प्यार करता हूँ। आप सभी खूबसूरत हैं, और इस रोमांचक सफ़र में साथ चलने के लिए मैं आप सभी का तहे दिल से शुक्रिया अदा करता हूँ। मुझे शुभकामनाएँ दें, और मैं आपसे अगले वीडियो में मिलूँगा! चलो जंग शुरू करते हैं।

ब्रेट्स्की ने अपने शीशे के चश्मे ठीक किए जैसे ही *गोल्डन मिराज* की नीयन लाइटें रेगिस्तानी रात में चमक उठीं। उसके बगल में, ब्लफ़—एक दुबला-पतला संशयवादी, जिसका पोकर चेहरा पत्थर से तराशा हुआ था—अपने पैर घसीट रहा था। "स्लॉट मशीनें नकली होती हैं," वह बुदबुदाया।

"सिर्फ़ तब जब तुम्हें सुनना न आता हो," ब्रेट्स्की ने अपने सिर पर थपथपाते हुए जवाब दिया। "आज रात, मैं तुम्हें स्पिन का विज्ञान दिखाता हूँ।"

अंदर, कसीनो में गड़गड़ाहट गूंज रही थी। घंटियाँ, चमकती रोशनियाँ, हताशा की खुशबू। ब्रेट्स्की स्पोर्ट्स बार के पास पुरानी स्लॉट मशीनों की कतार की ओर सीधा बढ़ा। "'लूनर लक 7'। शहर की सबसे ढीली मशीनें। लेकिन सिर्फ़ यही आधी रात को बजती है," उसने फुसफुसाते हुए एक टूटी-फूटी, बेकार मशीन की ओर इशारा किया जिस पर चेरी का डेकल टूटा हुआ था।

आधी रात हो गई। ब्रेट्स्की ने एक ताज़ा बीस का सिक्का डाला, और तीसरे स्पिन पर—**जैकपॉट**। सायरन बजने लगे, सिक्कों की बारिश होने लगी। ब्लफ़ का जबड़ा खुला का खुला रह गया।

"शुरुआती किस्मत," ब्लफ़ ने उपहास किया, लेकिन अगली मशीन पर बैठते ही उसका हाथ काँप रहा था।

फिर *दूसरी* जीत हुई। फिर तीसरी।

लेकिन कुछ बदल गया।

उनके पीछे एक गहरे रंग का सूट पहने आदमी दिखाई दिया, जिसके कान में इयरपीस और क्लिपबोर्ड था। "कुछ देर के लिए थोड़ा हटकर बात करना चाहोगे?" उसने पूछा। ब्रेट्स्की मुस्कुराया।

उन्हें पीछे वाले कमरे में ले जाया गया—न सुरक्षा, न लाउंज। बस एक लाल दरवाज़ा जिस पर कोई साइनबोर्ड नहीं था।

अंदर, धुआँ हवा में तैर रहा था। एक गोल मेज़। कैलकुलेटर जैसी आँखों वाले सात लोग उन्हें घूर रहे थे।

"तुम्हें बाधाओं को पार नहीं करना था," मखमली सूट पहने एक महिला ने कहा। "तुम्हें *पैटर्न* नहीं ढूँढ़ना था।"

ब्लफ़ ने निगल लिया। "कौन सा पैटर्न?"

ब्रेट्स्की गंभीर दिखे। "स्लॉट खेल नहीं हैं। वे **परीक्षण द्वार** हैं।"

ब्लफ़ की कुर्सी हिल गई—*ज़मीन पर टिक गई*। कमरा घूमने लगा, नीचे मशीनें घिसटने लगीं।

और जैसे ही ब्लफ़ ने ब्रेट्स्की का नाम पुकारा—

**लाल दरवाज़ा ज़ोर से बंद हो गया।**
**बत्ती बुझ गई।**
**एक आवाज़ गूँजी: "अगला चरण शुरू हो जाए।"**

ब्रेट्स्की कौन है? ब्रेट्स्की एक पेशेवर जुआरी है, जो वेगास मैट, ब्लफ़, डेगेनडाल्ट, मिस्टर हैंड पे या लेडी लक मुख्यालय जैसे प्राचीन दिग्गजों की तरह है! हालाँकि, इन दिग्गजों के विपरीत, ब्रेट्स्की के पास हज़ारों सालों का प्राचीन ज्ञान है, जो बुजुर्गों ने इकट्ठा किया था, जिसमें स्लॉट मशीन, रूलेट, ब्लैकजैक, क्रेप्स, बबल क्रेप्स, पोकर और बैकारेट जैसे कौशल शामिल हैं। एक पेशेवर जुआरी के रूप में ब्रेट्स्की का लक्ष्य सरल है: जुए से कमाए गए धन का उपयोग करके पूरे लास वेगास पर कब्ज़ा करना। विश्व प्रभुत्व में उनके सफ़र का समर्थन करने के लिए सदस्यता लें।

pt-BR.title: Ensinando Bluff a Jogar Caça-Níqueis!
pt-BR.description:
Estou dando um sorteio de US$ 50.000 que você NÃO vai querer perder!: http://codebrettski.com

Estamos DE VOLTA ao Cassino... com o cara em pessoa, Bluff! Estou mostrando a esse cara como jogar caça-níqueis, como gerenciá-los e como IMPRIMIR pagamentos manuais! Muito obrigado a todos por curtirem, se inscreverem e deixarem suas opiniões nos comentários. Mesmo que estejam me provocando, eu ainda amo vocês. Vocês são todos lindos, e eu realmente aprecio cada um de vocês por embarcar nessa jornada maluca. Me desejem sorte, e nos vemos na próxima! Vamos à guerra.

Brettski ajustou seus óculos escuros espelhados enquanto as luzes de neon do *Golden Mirage* pulsavam na noite do deserto. Ao lado dele, Bluff — um cético magro com uma cara de pôquer esculpida em pedra — arrastava os pés. "Caça-níqueis são manipulados", murmurou.

"Só se você não souber *como* ouvir", respondeu Brettski, batendo na lateral da cabeça. "Esta noite, eu te mostro a ciência da rodada."

Lá dentro, o cassino rugia. Sinos, luzes piscando, o cheiro do desespero. Brettski seguiu em linha reta para uma fileira de máquinas caça-níqueis antigas perto do bar esportivo. "As 'Lunar Luck 7s'. As máquinas mais fáceis da cidade. Mas só *esta* canta à meia-noite", sussurrou ele, apontando para uma máquina surrada e mal-amada com um adesivo de cereja rachado.

A meia-noite soou. Brettski colocou uma nota de vinte, e na terceira rodada — **JACKPOT**. Sirenes soaram, moedas choveram. O queixo de Bluff caiu.

"Sorte de principiante", zombou Bluff, mas sua mão tremia ao se sentar na máquina seguinte.

Então veio a *segunda* vitória. Depois, uma terceira.

Mas algo mudou.

Um homem de terno escuro, com fone de ouvido e prancheta, apareceu atrás deles. "Se importaria de se afastar para uma palavrinha?", perguntou. Brettski deu um sorriso forçado.

Eles foram conduzidos a uma sala nos fundos — não era segurança, não era um salão. Apenas uma porta vermelha sem sinalização.

Lá dentro, fumaça pairava no ar. Uma mesa redonda. Sete pessoas com olhos de calculadoras os encaravam.

"Você não deveria ter vencido as probabilidades", disse uma mulher de terno de veludo. "Você não deveria ter encontrado o *padrão*."

Bluff engoliu em seco. "Que padrão?"

Brettski parecia sério. "Os caça-níqueis não são jogos. São **testes de portas**."

A cadeira de Bluff deu um solavanco — *caiu no chão*. A sala começou a girar, com as máquinas rangendo embaixo.

E assim que Bluff gritou o nome de Brettski—

**A porta vermelha se fechou com força.**
**Luzes apagadas.**
**Uma voz ecoou: "Que comece a próxima fase."**

I made a Pokemon board game and challenged Peter, @shepskydad, and Captain Kidd to compete! Which Poketuber will be the first to assemble a team and obtain all 8 gym badges in this mario party style Pokemon game?
